          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-doreen-miller" title="Ms Doreen Miller">Baroness Miller of Hendon</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Minister gave a very brief answer, which was somewhat amusing in certain parts. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
